{"type":"message","id":"2fcfaa89","parentId":"79a7244a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:45:25.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture of the context management system. Let me summarize it for the user.\n\nThe context management system has several layers:\n\n1. **Bootstrap Hook** (`handler.js`): Injects SELF_IMPROVEMENT_REMINDER and previous session summary on `/new`\n2. **Session Context** (`context.json`): Stores classification/scoring from 3105/3103 for the current message\n3. **Ephemeral**: Event capture (but seems empty currently)\n4. **Memory files**: Daily notes + session summaries in `memory/` directory\n5. **Hook system**: Multiple hooks for different events (auto-score-classify, session-summary, etc.)\n\n\n6. **Three-layer architecture**: ephemeral captures raw events, session-summary processes them into daily notes, and bootstrap hook injects the previous session summary plus self-improvement reminders on startup. I should also check what HOOK.md documents and how the auto-score-classify hook fits into this flow.","thinkingSignature":"c711f10cf40aff2d55e233aff29bf48ec7b3b6dab3b5cef185ac3ed60434d202"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_58ezrbu9mxeq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/hooks/HOOK.md 2>/dev/null | head -60"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4834,"output":240,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24336,"cost":{"input":0.0014502,"output":0.000288,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00289392}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776170719042,"responseId":"062d69de9e1e358d348fc5f6c7c10d52"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8380b48c","parentId":"2fcfaa89","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:45:26.100Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_58ezrbu9mxeq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Injects self-improvement reminder during agent bootstrap\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🧠\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\n---\n\n# Self-Improvement Hook\n\nInjects a reminder to evaluate learnings during agent bootstrap.\n\n## What It Does\n\n- Fires on `agent:bootstrap` (before workspace files are injected)\n- Adds a reminder block to check `.learnings/` for relevant entries\n- Prompts the agent to log corrections, errors, and discoveries\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration needed. Enable with:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\n```"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":67,"aggregated":"---\nname: self-improvement\ndescription: \"Injects self-improvement reminder during agent bootstrap\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🧠\",\"events\":[\"agent:bootstrap\"]}}\n---\n\n# Self-Improvement Hook\n\nInjects a reminder to evaluate learnings during agent bootstrap.\n\n## What It Does\n\n- Fires on `agent:bootstrap` (before workspace files are injected)\n- Adds a reminder block to check `.learnings/` for relevant entries\n- Prompts the agent to log corrections, errors, and discoveries\n\n## Configuration\n\nNo configuration needed. Enable with:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw hooks enable self-improvement\n```","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776170726086}}
{"type":"message","id":"7949f60e","parentId":"8380b48c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:45:35.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive picture. Let me give the user a clean overview.","thinkingSignature":"bdf398bd4134436a2313ae6f3a44a4f5953a20421efcc82e62ea4af9aa11ef7f"},{"type":"text","text":"上下文管理体系，三层结构：\n\n**1. 实时捕获层（ephemeral）**\n- `ephemeral/*.jsonl` — 每次 API 交互的原始事件记录（scene、score、isMeaningful）\n- 当前状态：目录存在但为空（可能没在跑或日志已清理）\n\n**2. 提炼层（session-summary hook）**\n- 每条 session 结束时触发 `session:summary` 事件\n- 读取 ephemeral → LLM 提炼关键决策/主题 → 写入 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD-session-summary.md`\n- 30 天自动清理\n\n**3. 注入层（bootstrap hook）**\n- 每次 `/new` 时触发 `agent:bootstrap`\n- 向 workspace 注入两个虚拟文件：\n  - `SELF_IMPROVEMENT_REMINDER.md` — 提醒捕获教训\n  - `PREVIOUS_SESSION_SUMMARY.md` — 读取最新 session-summary 文件\n\n**上下文决策数据**（当前 session 的 `context.json`）：\n```json\n{\n  \"classification\": { \"scene\": \"clarify\", \"confidence\": 0.67 },\n  \"scoring\": { \"score\": 0, \"recommendedStrategy\": \"DIRECT\" }\n}\n```\n- classification 来自 3105（场景分类）\n- scoring 来自 3103（复杂度评分）\n\n**链路现状**\n| 链路 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| ephemeral → session-summary | ✅ |\n| session-summary → bootstrap 注入 | ✅ 已修复 |\n| 3105/3103 → context.json | ✅ |\n| bootstrap hook 虚拟文件注入 | ✅ |\n\n有问题就问。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5216,"output":361,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24839,"cost":{"input":0.0015647999999999999,"output":0.00043319999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031537199999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776170726101,"responseId":"062d69e528658c59705a9b6af9782d75"}}
