{"type":"message","id":"3b3f16e5","parentId":"99ebf835","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:49:32.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the current crons. Now let me add the new cron for pruning old summaries. I'll schedule it weekly on Sunday at 4:00 AM (Asia/Shanghai), after the memory-maintain cron.\n\nI need to create a cron job that:\n- Runs a Node.js script to prune old summaries\n- Is an isolated agentTurn that runs the prune script and logs results\n\nActually, looking at how the existing crons work, the `memory-maintain` and `memory-keeper` send systemEvent to main session, while `wiki-learn` runs in isolated mode.\n\nFor the prune script, I should run it as an isolated agentTurn that executes the script and logs the result.\n\n\nI'll set it up as an isolated agentTurn cron that triggers the prune script.","thinkingSignature":"908aed9f6cc27483562b72db7be1a8565fa214d3eb9b1ec6c817ca518b49e36f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dsecqb44282l_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"summary-pruner","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 4 * * 0","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行以下命令并报告输出：\n```\nnode /home/ai/.openclaw/scripts/prune-old-summaries.js\n```\n不要做任何其他事情，只执行命令并返回输出结果。"},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"description":"每周日凌晨 4:00 清理 30 天前的 session-summary 文件（独立于 session-summary hook，作为备份保障）"}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18218,"output":335,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37815,"cost":{"input":0.0054654,"output":0.00040199999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007023119999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776170962099,"responseId":"062d6ad12f875eb8ef265110349ab823"}}
