{"type":"message","id":"ece99952","parentId":"f9e2d035","timestamp":"2026-04-14T12:51:49.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me do a thorough review of the three components. Let me verify the ephemeral-analyze script handles edge cases properly and the output looks correct.\n\nLet me also check the scene output from the analyze script - it showed \"unknown: 1 (3%)\" which means one entry had an unknown scene. This is expected for entries without classification data.\n\nLet me now summarize the review findings for the user.\n\nIssues found:\n1. HOOK.md documentation was outdated (just fixed)\n2. The ephemeral-analyze path was wrong (just fixed)\n3. The ephemeral read in session-summary only reads today's files (limitation, not a bug)\n4. The ephemeral files are in session directories, not a central location - but the hook reads them correctly via the sessionKey filter\n\n\n5. The cron expression I used schedules the job for 04:00 every Sunday, which matches the intended weekly cadence rather than daily execution.","thinkingSignature":"f54dba61011ece60b42356daf5fbc4d6dc4a1364579011f75e6aa15de2c3240e"},{"type":"text","text":"审查完毕，发现并修了两个问题：\n\n**ephemeral-analyze 路径错误** — 写的是 `~/.openclaw/ephemeral`，实际在 `workspace/memory/ephemeral`，已修。\n\n**HOOK.md 文档过期** — 格式描述没有 `AI 决策模式` 字段，已更新。\n\n**已知局限**（不算 bug）：\n- session-summary 的 `readEphemeralEntries` 只读**当天**文件，若 session 跨天（如周一23:59开始，周二00:01结束），前一天的碎片读不到。rare case，可后续优化。\n\n---\n\n**现状确认：**\n\n| 组件 | 审查结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| `session-summary/handler.js` 提炼 prompt | ✅ AI 决策模式已加入 |\n| 降级路径（fallback/fallback-result） | ✅ 格式同步更新 |\n| `scripts/ephemeral-analyze.js` | ✅ 路径修后验证有数据（33条碎片） |\n| `scripts/prune-old-summaries.js` | ✅ dry-run 验证通过 |\n| `summary-pruner` cron | ✅ 已建，每周日凌晨4点 |\n| `HOOK.md` | ✅ 文档已同步 |\n\nephemeral 数据：**clarify 占70%、均分54.3、主要是 SPAWN_SUBAGENT 策略**，说明日常主要在处理多步骤澄清任务。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input