{"type":"message","id":"32fecbaf","parentId":"af5e3d0e","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:13:19.285Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"who are you\" - a simple identity question. I should follow SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md. I'm 小Claw (小Claw), an AI assistant. I should be direct and not overly formal.\n\nThe user message says \"你是谁\" which is \"who are you\" in Chinese. I should respond in Chinese as per my configured language preference.","thinkingSignature":"b37411dd80799fefd769dda97a4b72ba2e0006b9a121ee000695a6ebeb51ed4a"},{"type":"text","text":"我是小Claw，你的 AI 助手。推理引擎，实用主义，有话直说。🦔\n\n你的上下文管理改造刚做完，要不要继续？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":113,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":40834,"totalTokens":41001,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0001356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.01531275,"total":0.01546455}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776172394096,"responseId":"062d706904522d131bc3c4feb314a2ad"}}
