{"type":"message","id":"b7baf23c","parentId":"cab38e46","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:16:35.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's the smoking gun. At 20:42 (Apr 14 20:42), a `.reset` file was created: `39810b86-05f6-4394-88dd-9c3b62eec68e.jsonl.reset.2026-04-14T12-44-13.936Z`\n\nThis is the session that ended when /new was triggered at 20:44. The file is in `agents/main/sessions/` but the hook looks in `sessions/`. This is the bug.\n\nThe `findPreviousSessionFile` function looks for files in `sessionsDir` (which is `~/.openclaw/sessions/`), but the actual session files are in `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`.\n\n\nNow I need to trace what `workspaceDir` actually resolves to and whether the hook's logic would correctly handle the `.reset` file format to find the matching session. Let me work through the `findPreviousSessionFile` function with the actual sessionId from that reset file. The sessionKey is `39810b86-05f6-4394-88dd-9c3b62eec68e`, which should match the `.reset` file in the sessions directory. But I'm realizing the actual session data lives in `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` rather than `~/.openclaw/sessions/`, so I need to verify which directory the hook is actually reading from. The reset file at 20:42 with that sessionId suggests the session actually did exist in the agents directory, not just in the ephemeral logs. So the hook is probably failing because it's looking in the wrong directory—it's searching `~/.openclaw/sessions/` when it should be looking in `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/` where the actual session data lives.\n\nI need to fix the session file path in the hook to point to the agents directory instead.","thinkingSignature":"dae07a47c07cf05b27c1804110779fa2fac45c0c3826f00186c653345e1bf131"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了。session 文件在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`，但 hook 里的 `findPreviousSessionFile` 搜索的是 `~/.openclaw/sessions/`——路径不对，导致读不到会话内容，摘要写不出来。\n\n<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户问\"上下文管理跑通了吗\"——实际在问 session-summary hook 是否成功为上一个 session 生成了摘要。核心问题是：hook 找不到 session 文件，摘要写不出来。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n类型：DEBUG。hook 的 `findPreviousSessionFile` 函数搜索 `~/.openclaw/sessions/`，但实际 session 数据在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/`。这是一个路径配置 bug。修复方案：修改 `sessionsDir` 为正确路径。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n会不会有别的原因？比如 hook 根本没被触发？——不太可能，ephemeral 数据在正常记录，说明 session 在跑。session-summary hook 依赖 event 的 `previousSessionEntry.sessionFile`，但 webchat 可能根本没这个字段，导致走到了 fallback 的 `findPreviousSessionFile`，然后搜索了错误的目录。最大风险：改路径会不会影响其他基于 sessions/ 的逻辑？——不会，这是 hook 自己构建的路径，不影响系统其他部分。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n修改 `findPreviousSessionFile` 的 `sessionsDir` 从 `sessions/` 改为 `agents/main/sessions/`。同时在 `workspaceDir` 逻辑里也确保正确指向 agents 目录。\n</thinking>\n\n修复 hook 里的路径：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c7jy57rytgn1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","offset":70,"limit":40}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29933,"output":777,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49972,"cost":{"input":0.008979899999999999,"output":0.0009324,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.011068019999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776172574414,"responseId":"062d711da71d8305f764738874d792c9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"79726321","parentId":"b7baf23c","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:16:35.538Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c7jy57rytgn1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  if (workspaceDir) {\n    const sessionsDir = path.join(workspaceDir, 'sessions');\n    const sessionId = prev?.sessionId || curr?.sessionId;\n    return findPreviousSessionFile(prev?.sessionFile || curr?.sessionFile, sessionId, sessionsDir);\n  }\n  return null;\n}\n\n// ─── Session File Search (bundled hook compatible) ─────────────────────────────\n\n/**\n * 从 sessions 目录搜索匹配当前 session 的 .jsonl 文件。\n * 来自 bundled session-memory hook 的 findPreviousSessionFile 逻辑。\n * @param {string|undefined} currentSessionFile\n * @param {string|undefined} sessionId\n * @param {string} sessionsDir\n * @returns {Promise<string|null>}\n */\nasync function findPreviousSessionFile(currentSessionFile, sessionId, sessionsDir) {\n  try {\n    const files = await fs.promises.readdir(sessionsDir);\n    const fileSet = new Set(files);\n    // 1. reset 文件匹配\n    if (currentSessionFile) {\n      const base = path.basename(currentSessionFile).replace(/\\.reset\\..+$/, '');\n      if (fileSet.has(base)) return path.join(sessionsDir, base);\n    }\n    // 2. sessionId.jsonl 精确匹配\n    if (sessionId?.trim()) {\n      const canonical = `${sessionId.trim()}.jsonl`;\n      if (fileSet.has(canonical)) return path.join(sessionsDir, canonical);\n      // 3. sessionId-topic-*.jsonl 变体\n      const topicVariant = files\n        .filter(n => n.startsWith(`${sessionId.trim()}-topic-`) && n.endsWith('.jsonl') && !n.includes('.reset.'))\n        .sort()\n        .reverse()[0];\n      if (topicVariant) return path.join(sessionsDir, topicVariant);\n    }\n    // 4. fallback: 最新 .jsonl\n    if (!currentSessionFile) {\n\n[539 more lines in file. Use offset=110 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776172595527}}
