{"type":"message","id":"c7c34dc3","parentId":"98d44b39","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:19:12.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also check what sessionFile value the hook receives. Since we can't easily trigger /new to test, let me verify by checking the hook logic more carefully.Actually, the best test is to manually simulate what the hook would do. Let me write a quick test script to verify the findPreviousSessionFile logic works with the actual reset file.But actually, we should also think about whether `prev?.sessionFile` would actually be set for webchat sessions. Looking at the context.json:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n  \"classification\": {...},\n  \"scoring\": {...},\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-14T12:44:58.812Z\",\n  \"messagePreview\": \"[Tue 2026-04-14 20:44 GMT+8] 看看你的上下文管理\"\n}\n```\n\nThere's no `previousSessionEntry` in this context.json. So `resolveSessionFile` falls through to `findPreviousSessionFile` with `currentSessionFile = undefined` and `sessionId = undefined`. But wait—the HOOK.md says it should have `previousSessionEntry`, so maybe this context.json is from the current session, not the previous one.\n\nThe HOOK.md specifies that the hook depends on `context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile` to read the session that just ended. For the current webchat session at 20:44, that field doesn't seem to exist. Let me trace through the handler logic more carefully—if `event.type === \"command\"` and `event.action === \"new\"`, then `resolveSessionFile` gets called. For webchat sessions, the gateway might not be injecting `previousSessionEntry` at all.\n\nIf both `currentSessionFile` and `sessionId` are undefined, the function just returns null, which means the hook can't find the session file. The fix needs to handle this case—when there's no previous session file or ID, I should look for the most recent reset file as a fallback instead of returning null.","thinkingSignature":"8fc368e303b87c2758a9fc82d61203b5c47e90695d333c68e938c20ff511f10d"},{"type":"text","text":"还需要处理 `sessionId` 也为空的情况（webchat 特性）。加一个兜底：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_009mwcdqk34y_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js","edits":[{"oldText":"    // 6. fallback: 最新 .jsonl（非 reset，仅当前 session 自己）\n    if (!currentSessionFile) {\n      const latest = files\n        .filter(n => n.endsWith('.jsonl') && !n.includes('.reset.'))\n        .sort()\n        .reverse()[0];\n      if (latest) return path.join(sessionsDir, latest);\n    }","newText":"    // 6. 完全兜底：最新 reset 文件（webchat 可能 sessionId/currentSessionFile 均为空）\n    if (!currentSessionFile && !sessionId?.trim()) {\n      const latestReset = files\n        .filter(n => n.includes('.reset.'))\n        .sort()\n        .reverse()[0];\n      if (latestReset) return path.join(sessionsDir, latestReset);\n    }\n\n    // 7. fallback: 最新 .jsonl（非 reset，仅当前 session 自己）\n    if (!currentSessionFile) {\n      const latest = files\n        .filter(n => n.endsWith('.jsonl') && !n.includes('.reset.'))\n        .sort()\n        .reverse()[0];\n      if (latest) return path.join(sessionsDir, latest);\n    }"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38574,"output":768,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58604,"cost":{"input":0.0115722,"output":0.0009216,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013649519999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776172734705,"responseId":"062d71be45aec6f66c86f8792e7bab34"}}
{"type":"message","id":"82d40143","parentId":"c7c34dc3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:19:12.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_009mwcdqk34y_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /home/ai/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/handler.js."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 127         .reverse()[0];\n 128       if (idResetVariant) return path.join(sessionsDir, idResetVariant);\n 129     }\n 130 \n-131     // 6. fallback: 最新 .jsonl（非 reset，仅当前 session 自己）\n+131     // 6. 完全兜底：最新 reset 文件（webchat 可能 sessionId/currentSessionFile 均为空）\n+132     if (!currentSessionFile && !sessionId?.trim()) {\n+133       const latestReset = files\n+134         .filter(n => n.includes('.reset.'))\n+135         .sort()\n+136         .reverse()[0];\n+137       if (latestReset) return path.join(sessionsDir, latestReset);\n+138     }\n+139 \n+140     // 7. fallback: 最新 .jsonl（非 reset，仅当前 session 自己）\n 132     if (!currentSessionFile) {\n 133       const latest = files\n 134         .filter(n => n.endsWith('.jsonl') && !n.includes('.reset.'))\n 135         .sort()\n     ...","firstChangedLine":131},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776172752865}}
