{"type":"message","id":"99be80ae","parentId":"d7d748e8","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:20:29.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"do I need to /new now?\" - they're asking if they should trigger a /new to test if the session-summary hook fix works.","thinkingSignature":"f5fc0e8b683773df0b37811726371648bf798083fd6e3718660fbaec7f00d9ec"},{"type":"text","text":"不需要。下次自然 `/new` 就行，hook 会自动跑。\n\n如果想现在就验证 `findPreviousSessionFile` 逻辑是否找到 reset 文件，可以手动跑一下分析脚本试：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qoxck6wcel84_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node --input-type=module << 'EOF'\nimport fs from 'node:fs';\nimport path from 'node:path';\n\nconst sessionsDir = path.join(process.env.HOME, '.openclaw', 'agents', 'main', 'sessions');\nconst files = await fs.promises.readdir(sessionsDir);\n\n// 最新 reset 文件\nconst latestReset = files.filter(n => n.includes('.reset.')).sort().reverse()[0];\nconsole.log('最新 reset 文件:', latestReset);\n\n// 最新活跃文件\nconst latestActive = files.filter(n => n.endsWith('.jsonl') && !n.includes('.reset.')).sort().reverse()[0];\nconsole.log('最新活跃文件:', latestActive);\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":240,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":34992,"totalTokens":54548,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.000288,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0.013122,"total":0.01458192}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776172820695,"responseId":"062d7213f436b5ff68c4e22f17b26cdf"}}
